# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  PROJECT TITLE — Add your project name below (edit this line)                ║
# ║  The Episteme Project                                                        ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
#
# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  USER_SPECIFIED — Project-specific ignores (episteme)                        ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
#
# HOW TO ADD ITEMS
# ----------------
# • One pattern per line. Blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored by git.
# • No quotes; just the pattern. Leading/trailing spaces can cause surprises.
#
# FILES
#   my-secret.txt          → ignores this file anywhere in the repo
#   /root-only.txt         → ignores only at repository root
#   subdir/other.txt       → ignores subdir/other.txt (any depth)
#
# FOLDERS
#   myfolder/              → trailing slash = ignore the whole directory (any depth)
#   /build/                → only the build/ folder at repo root
#   **/node_modules/       → node_modules at any depth (same as node_modules/)
#
# WILDCARDS
#   *        matches any string except /
#   **       matches any string including / (any depth)
#   ?        matches a single character
#   [abc]    matches one character: a, b, or c
#   [0-9]    matches one digit
#
# EXAMPLES
#   *.log                  → all .log files
#   *.tmp
#   temp-*                 → temp-foo, temp-bar, etc.
#   **/dist/               → every dist/ folder
#   .env*                  → .env, .env.local, .env.production
#   *.local                → anything ending in .local
#
# NEGATION (exceptions)
#   Use ! to UN-ignore something that a previous rule would ignore.
#   *.log                  → ignore all logs
#   !important.log         → but keep important.log
#   .vscode/               → ignore whole folder
#   !.vscode/settings.json → but track this file
#
# Add your patterns below (uncomment and edit):
# --------------------------------------------
project-ideas.ai
# my-local-config.json
# secrets/
# *.local
